28:20.893 --> 28:22.215
time to sleep? Damn little. Damn little. All 
right, for my service, I don't mind being

28:27.175 --> 28:39.995
braggadocious about it, but there is my, there are 
my annual reports for my two years, practically

28:27.175 --> 28:39.995
two years of tenure of office. There they are right 
there. Where we go into a whole lot of stuff. The

28:45.443 --> 28:47.046
Native industry. Tell me how you got along with the 
Samoan people. I got along with Samoan people

28:50.005 --> 28:53.249
because I was firm and I was fair. When I set up the 
