know about all this other stuff. Well, of course, 
there's instances I could go on and elaborate and

42:43.457 --> 42:50.748
so forth and so on, you know what I mean? Now... Did 
you think that Europe, that you did, that, uh, The

42:55.375 --> 43:04.187
most difficult chore was to getting the Samoan 
people to get used to the war effort and all those

42:55.375 --> 43:04.187
changes? They were not. They were for a little 
