because they knew I was fair and I was stern. Yeah. 
Now, a lot of times there's some Marine officer who

43:14.621 --> 43:20.650
comes right in the seat for some native that I had in 
the jail. Mm-hmm. So, uh, I'd look at him, I says, do

43:24.653 --> 43:31.880
I ever come over to your 50 caliber group and tell 
you how to run your battery? He said, no, sir. I

43:32.560 --> 43:33.621
said, why don't you come over here? I said, you're 
