45:22.694 --> 45:28.101
says, you people must think I'm sitting on an 
Evinrude motor hill. I'm going to shove off here

45:29.422 --> 45:32.146
myself without a pilot. And with that, he did.

45:36.751 --> 45:37.172
That's right. Anyhow, so much for Samoa. And I 
returned to the United States.

